  "description": "bodyFreq=40Hz (E0 territory — below standard tuning, permanent rumble). Single divider: ÷2 only. bodyLevel=0.6 — the body is louder than the MIDI voice. Per OWL-II: this is duophonic. One voice follows your fingers; one does not. You compose against a 40Hz wall that never moves. Learn to write melodies inside a fixed floor.",
